    24: "Imagine yourself, summer 2024. The past two years being full of politic turmoil, with BLM, the Trump vs. Harris campaign, Israel-Palestine conflict reigniting on the world stage with college campuses being one of the main actors on the other side of the camera. Invigorated, frustrated, and inspired to act, I knew that one of the most important things during times like these is learning the full picture; the truth. To be able to strip the chaos into what it is.",
